line is really three years.

04:09.310 --> 04:10.675
So...

04:10.710 --> 04:13.474
do you need a lavwer?

04:15.320 --> 04:17.686
We're plea bargaining
with Geneva Pine.

04:17.720 --> 04:19.039
They offered Cary
three years.

04:19.090 --> 04:21.513
We're wondering what
the SA's bottom line is.

04:21.560 --> 04:24.552
Well, you know that it would be
unethical for me to answer that.

04:24.590 --> 04:26.592
(phone rings)

04:28.100 --> 04:30.068
Sorry, would you excuse me?

04:30.100 --> 04:31.897
Hello.

04:31.930 --> 04:33.739
JACKIE:
Hello, Alicia, it's Jackie.

04:33.770 --> 04:34.737
Uh, yes.

04:34.770 --> 04:36.067
Jackie, I'm at work.

04:36.100 --> 04:37.328
Can we talk later?

04:37.370 --> 04:38.598
No, unfortunately, we can't.

04:38.640 --> 04:40.403
