05:13.080 --> 05:14.809
WOMAN: You're needed
in court, Your Honor.

05:14.840 --> 05:17.547
Uh, hold onto them for me.
I'll be there.

05:19.750 --> 05:21.411
SHERIFF:
All rise. Court is in session.

05:21.450 --> 05:23.384
Everybody sit.

05:23.420 --> 05:25.547
Ms. Lockhart, where
are we on the plea?

05:25.590 --> 05:28.582
