05:33.430 --> 05:36.399
but I want you to know
this jury will be seated today.

05:36.430 --> 05:38.398
Let's go. Bring 'em in.

05:38.430 --> 05:40.591
(school bell ringing)

05:49.480 --> 05:53.041
Mrs. Florrick, good.
Maybe you can help us with this?

05:53.080 --> 05:55.116
Hey, Mom.
Grace.

05:55.150 --> 05:57.118
"Dear Coach Linklater,

05:57.150 --> 06:00.381
"As I wrote yesterday, Grace
needs to be excused from running

06:00.420 --> 06:03.150
"in PE. because she's
contracted a cold.

06:03.190 --> 06:05.158
"If you make her
run again,

06:05.190 --> 06:07.658
"I will personally come
down to your office

06:07.700 --> 06:11.124
