most probably bleed out.

06:21.210 --> 06:23.144
"Thank you for your concern,

06:23.180 --> 06:25.102
Alicia Florrick."

06:25.150 --> 06:27.778
Did you write this,
Mrs. Florrick?

06:27.820 --> 06:29.549
Okay.

06:29.590 --> 06:32.150
Just to be clear--
it was a joke.

06:32.190 --> 06:33.987
Have you ever seen
Darkness at Noon?

06:34.020 --> 06:36.159
No._
I was just

06:36.190 --> 06:39.182
