the hero makes to someone.

06:39.230 --> 06:40.697
I wrote it down

06:40.730 --> 06:43.119
to make Grace laugh.
It was just between us.

06:43.170 --> 06:45.627
It was never meant
to be delivered...

06:45.670 --> 06:47.137
to them.
Yes,

06:47.170 --> 06:48.194
and yet
here it is

06:48.240 --> 06:49.867
on my desk.
Alicia is a

06:49.910 --> 06:53.004
good mother.
She would never stab a teacher.

06:53.040 --> 06:55.179
Thank you, Jackie.
Uh, just to be clear--

06:55.210 --> 06:56.973
it was a joke.
About

06:57.010 --> 06:59.717
killing a teacher?
It wasn't meant...

06:59.750 --> 07:01.172
