I showed her the note.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.650
To ask if this
was protected.

07:11.690 --> 07:13.954
And you laughed.
You knew it was a joke.
I asked

07:14.000 --> 07:16.093
ifI could keep it.
To show it
to her husband. You said

07:16.130 --> 07:18.598
