It's not Ms. Slavick's

07:18.630 --> 07:20.632
fault she brought
it to me. It's

07:20.670 --> 07:22.160
the responsibility
of all teachers

07:22.200 --> 07:24.236
to bring me threats
without fail.

07:24.270 --> 07:26.238
This is a threat.

07:26.270 --> 07:28.238
It's a joke.
We don't like jokes
like that here.

07:28.280 --> 07:31.545
I understand.
It won't happen again.

07:31.580 --> 07:33.468
Guys, I think we
should leave it there.

07:33.520 --> 07:35.249
JACKIE:
Good, then that's it.
It was all just

07:35.280 --> 07:37.510
a misunderstanding.

07:37.550 --> 07:39.484
DIANE:
And you think
you can be impartial

07:39.520 --> 07:41.112
during this trial?
MAN: I think I can do

07:41.160 --> 07:42.923
my best.
Mm-hmm. This juror

07:42.960 --> 07:44.825
