So we have a

08:32.140 --> 08:34.279
problem?
Cary's trial.
I think

08:34.310 --> 08:36.232
if it's a guilty verdict,
we don't say anything.

08:36.280 --> 08:38.771
We can't comment while
the verdict's under appeal.

08:38.810 --> 08:41.745
They're not gonna
let you get away with that.
