08:46.290 --> 08:48.281
Uh, no, you don't. Not when
you're the body woman.

08:48.320 --> 08:51.255
She's right, Eli. And you'd know
that if you'd been with us more.
Oh,

08:51.290 --> 08:53.053
come on, don't pull that one.
Let's be honest-_-
your focus is split.

08:53.100 --> 08:55.091
