This story is only going
to become a story...

08:55.130 --> 08:57.121
Eli, Weekly
Correspondent's on one.

08:57.170 --> 08:58.592
Oh. Here we go.

08:58.630 --> 08:59.938
They want to talk
about Cary's trial.

08:59.970 --> 09:01.267
Eli, you don't
get to decide this.

09:01.300 --> 09:03.302
We decide this.

09:03.340 --> 09:04.864
Hey, Brian,
it's Johnny.

09:04.910 --> 09:06.263
How are you?
Good. I have

09:06.310 --> 09:08.335
