bleed out like a pig?

09:22.660 --> 09:24.252
Uh, what?

09:24.290 --> 09:27.726
Did Alicia threaten to knife
one of her daughter's teachers?

09:27.760 --> 09:30.627
Brian, I...

09:30.670 --> 09:31.989
What are you
talking about?

09:32.030 --> 09:33.292
So that's an unequivocal no?

09:33.340 --> 09:35.194
Yes, it's a no.
Are you insane?

09:36.400 --> 09:37.936
Alicia.
I think

09:37.970 --> 09:39.904
