hear this.

09:39.940 --> 09:41.737
JOHNNY:
Uh, good talking
to you, Brian.

09:41.780 --> 09:44.078
Anytime you want to know about
flying saucers, call us, too.

09:44.110 --> 09:45.873
(chuckles)

09:45.910 --> 09:47.946
What was that?
Nothing, he-he...
We're good.

09:47.980 --> 09:49.379
He didn't even
mention Cary's trial.

09:49.420 --> 09:51.388
I think you'd better
tell Alicia what he asked.

09:51.420 --> 09:53.058
No, he was joking.

09:53.090 --> 09:54.717
Did you threaten
to murder

09:54.760 --> 09:56.216
one of your kid's
teachers and

09:56.260 --> 09:57.386
bleed him out
like a pig?

09:57.430 --> 09:59.648
(laughing)

10:05.330 --> 10:06.638
Alicia.

10:06.670 --> 10:10.106
Well, here's the thing.

10:22.790 --> 10:25.782
