10:25.820 --> 10:28.755
No, you can't call me.
Not at home.

10:28.790 --> 10:30.781
I can't leave him. I can't.

10:32.860 --> 10:34.657
I'm going now.

10:34.700 --> 10:37.919
I'm going.

10:37.970 --> 10:40.996
