on the stand or I'll crack up.

10:41.040 --> 10:44.009
Name and occupation, Detective?

10:44.040 --> 10:45.439
Gary Prima.

10:45.470 --> 10:47.131
I'm a detective with
the narcotics section

10:47.180 --> 10:49.375
of the Chicago
Police Department.

10:50.980 --> 10:52.242
Thank you,
Detective.

10:52.280 --> 10:54.145
And you had a
confidential informant

10:54.180 --> 10:56.273
record the defendant
committing this crime?
Objection,

10:56.320 --> 10:58.117
Your Honor.
Argumentative.

10:58.150 --> 11:00.015
That is correct.
Sustained.

11:00.060 --> 11:02.016
You had the defendant
record the defendant?

11:02.060 --> 11:03.186
The CI.
record the defendant?

11:03.230 --> 11:05.881
Yes. Sorry, yes.

11:05.930 --> 11:08.091
That's okay. Trey
Wagner was a member

11:08.130 --> 11:09.995
