is dead.

11:46.470 --> 11:49.268
So you may feel that
this tape is not worthy

11:49.300 --> 11:51.063
of your full
consideration

11:51.110 --> 11:53.078
because you're not
hearing both sides of it.

11:53.110 --> 11:54.771
But I leave
that to you.

11:54.810 --> 11:56.949
Now, Ms. Pine.
Ms. Pine?

11:56.980 --> 11:57.947
Yes.
Ms. Pine,

11:57.980 --> 11:59.072
you may continue.

11:59.110 --> 12:01.010
Yes, Your Honor.

12:01.050 --> 12:05.009
