13:36.180 --> 13:37.169
We've all done it.

13:39.250 --> 13:40.512
Okay, you need to get the note.

13:40.550 --> 13:42.518
That's the bottom line.
We can spin this,

13:42.550 --> 13:43.983
but you need
to get the note.

13:44.020 --> 13:46.511
Grace. Uh, we
need your help.

13:46.550 --> 13:49.314
Do you have civics today?
