DIANE: Detective,

14:12.280 --> 14:14.976
did you speak with Trey
Wagner four weeks ago?

14:15.020 --> 14:16.442
PRIMA:
I spoke to someone
who identified himself

14:16.480 --> 14:18.141
as Trey Wagner,

14:18.190 --> 14:20.385
but I wasn't...
I couldn't be... sure.

14:20.420 --> 14:25.028
But ASA Finn Polmar assured you
that it was Trey Wagner?

14:25.060 --> 14:27.199
Yes, he did.
