on the phone tell you

14:27.230 --> 14:28.458
that he had set up Cary Agos?

14:28.500 --> 14:30.092
Objection, Your Honor.
Hearsay.

14:30.130 --> 14:31.620
Your Honor, the
ASA has opened

14:31.670 --> 14:33.638
the door by presenting
hearsay testimony

14:33.670 --> 14:35.399
