they hurt her case.

14:41.340 --> 14:44.275
CUESTA:
Well, she's got you
there, ASA Pine.

14:44.310 --> 14:47.347
Overruled. _
You may answer, Detective.

14:47.380 --> 14:49.416
Yes. This person

14:49.450 --> 14:52.010
said that he had
set up Cary Agos.

14:52.050 --> 14:55.019
DIANE: And how did he do that?
By selectively turning
the wire on and off

14:55.060 --> 14:58.427
to make Mr. Agos' statements
seem more damning.
And did he say

14:58.460 --> 15:00.519
why he did that?
He said he
was afraid

15:00.560 --> 15:04.166
of Mr. Bishop, and he had
to get us someone lower.

15:04.200 --> 15:07.169
DIANE:
Meaning Cary. And how
long after he said this

15:07.200 --> 15:08.963
was Trey
Wagner killed?

15:09.000 --> 15:10.536
Objection.
Excuse me.
How long

15:10.570 --> 15:13.676
after this did Trey Wagner die
in a car accident

15:13.710 --> 15:17.100
that the police have
called suspicious?

15:17.150 --> 15:18.344
48 hours.
I see.

15:18.380 --> 15:19.574
Thank you,
Your Honor.

15:19.610 --> 15:22.215
Okay,
how exciting.

15:22.250 --> 15:25.947
And we are adjourned for lunch.

15:25.990 --> 15:28.959
* Sweet Caroline

15:28.990 --> 15:30.389
* Ba-ba

15:30.430 --> 15:31.988
* Ba, ba...

15:32.030 --> 15:33.122
MARISSA:
Foundit

15:33.160 --> 15:34.718
Uh, hold on, Grace. Hold on.

