"Grizzly Mom in Illinois
Race Shows Claws."

15:37.300 --> 15:38.221
Good headline.
Where is it?

15:38.270 --> 15:40.261
BuzzFeed.
Politics.

15:40.300 --> 15:42.268
"Don't get Alicia
Florrick angry.

15:42.300 --> 15:44.234
"It's reported
that Alicia Florrick

15:44.270 --> 15:46.067
"threatened a teacher
at her daughter's

15:46.110 --> 15:47.372
"tony high school
with violence

15:47.410 --> 15:49.537
