to work out while sick."

15:49.580 --> 15:52.276
It doesn't have
the note?
No, it doesn't.

15:52.310 --> 15:54.119
Hi. Sorry, Grace.
What did she say?

15:54.150 --> 15:55.549
She says she wants
to give you back the note,

15:55.580 --> 15:57.218
but first she wants
to meet you in person.

15:57.250 --> 15:58.979
What? Why?

15:59.020 --> 16:00.351
I don't know.
I think she wants to make sure

16:00.390 --> 16:02.085
you don't threaten
to kill someone again.

16:02.120 --> 16:04.384
Dear Lord...
I thought she was nice.

16:04.430 --> 16:05.488
Now I'm not so sure.

16:05.530 --> 16:07.088
(sighs)
Okay. I'll call her.

16:07.130 --> 16:08.495
Sorry to put you through this.

16:08.530 --> 16:11.021
Mom, you didn't. I did.
No.

16:11.070 --> 16:13.493
I need to stop joking.
They need to get
a sense of humor.

16:13.540 --> 16:17.135
(chuckles)
Okay. Love you. Bye.

16:18.510 --> 16:20.273
You're nice with your daughter.

16:20.310 --> 16:23.245
(phone rings)
Hi, Jon. What's wrong?

16:23.280 --> 16:25.373
Yeah, BuzzFeed.
The politics section.

16:26.750 --> 16:29.071
ELI:
That points
to a way out of this.

16:29.120 --> 16:31.680
Yeah, hang on a second.
I got Eli on speaker.
It points to a way out of this.

16:31.720 --> 16:33.483
We need to push you
as a grizzly mom.
Yeah,

16:33.520 --> 16:35.317
I agree. It's all about
how much you love your daughter.

16:35.360 --> 16:37.328
I tried to stab a teacher
because I love my daughter?

16:37.360 --> 16:40.329
ELI:
Alicia, are you joking? Remember
what I said about joking?

16:40.360 --> 16:43.488
JOHNNY:
If we leave it vague, then,
uh, we can argue grizzly mom.

16:43.530 --> 16:45.293
But the minute the note
is out there, then it becomes

16:45.330 --> 16:46.695
about knives and bleeding out.

16:46.730 --> 16:48.391
So you need to get that note.

16:48.440 --> 16:49.668
Yeah, I'm working
on it.
Uh-oh.

16:49.700 --> 16:53.409
I'm really starting
to hate those syllables.

16:53.440 --> 16:55.374
PRADY:
Are you asking me how
