JOHNNY: What are you watching?

16:58.450 --> 17:01.317
Frank Prady.
With the Correspondent board.
PRADY: Well, let me say this,

17:01.350 --> 17:03.341
if a teacher or a student
threatened to knife

17:03.390 --> 17:05.779
a teacher, yes,
