17:05.820 --> 17:07.685
Or her?
Yes.

17:07.720 --> 17:09.358
To the fullest extent
of the law.

17:09.390 --> 17:11.756
And, yes, if there were even
merely a written threat,

17:11.790 --> 17:14.156
I would prosecute.
School violence

17:14.200 --> 17:17.761
is too serious
to treat as a joke.
Alicia, he's coming after you.

17:17.800 --> 17:20.337
We need to use our oppo on him.
