17:20.370 --> 17:23.464
two sources that'll
say he's closeted.
_ _ Our _
fingerprints are never on it.

17:23.510 --> 17:25.808
JOHNNY: We point the reporter to
the source. They're starving
for it at this point anyway.

17:25.840 --> 17:28.536
ELI: If they don't go
for a Prady story, they'll go
after you for the knifing.

17:28.580 --> 17:30.844
Yeah, Alicia, we don't agree
