17:34.720 --> 17:38.417
Eli, please, we'll talk tonight.

17:45.760 --> 17:48.354
You gave them reasonable doubt.

17:48.400 --> 17:49.389
I know.

17:49.430 --> 17:51.227
Do you know
what to do?

17:51.270 --> 17:52.498
I do.
Good.

17:52.530 --> 17:53.394
Do it.

17:57.240 --> 17:59.435
We cannot
lose this.

18:05.610 --> 18:08.579
So?

18:08.620 --> 18:09.814
It's over between us?
