18:30.540 --> 18:31.768
Goody
for you.

18:31.810 --> 18:32.663
Who is it?

18:32.710 --> 18:34.701
Kalinda Sharma.

18:48.860 --> 18:49.383
(door opens)

18:49.420 --> 18:50.853
Let's go. Sidebar over.

18:50.890 --> 18:52.482
(sighs)

