not bars.

21:03.360 --> 21:05.521
Pancakes, not drinks.
Yes. And we...

21:05.560 --> 21:09.326
talk about... the law.

21:09.360 --> 21:11.521
Great. With accordion music.

21:11.570 --> 21:13.663
Well, unfortunately, accordion
music kind of turns me on.

21:13.700 --> 21:16.635
(chuckles)

21:18.640 --> 21:20.437
Okay. No music.

21:20.480 --> 21:21.833
I'll see you.

21:25.410 --> 21:27.378
So what the hell?

21:27.420 --> 21:30.344
Excuse me?
