to the press

21:30.390 --> 21:33.018
these two guys who said
they had an affair with
me? I thought we agreed...

21:33.050 --> 21:35.484
Wait, wait, what?
You leaked to the press...

21:35.520 --> 21:38.057
I did not.
O-Or your people.
Your handlers did it.

21:38.090 --> 21:40.081
Excuse me, we did not.
Do we have
an agreement

21:40.130 --> 21:42.849
or don't we? We said
we wouldn't smear each other.

21:42.900 --> 21:45.095
Wait a minute. Who's the one
who went to the Correspondent

21:45.130 --> 21:48.634
and told them
that I should be prosecuted?
Are you serious?

21:48.670 --> 21:51.036
You wanted to roll_
a one-day story into a fight.

21:51.070 --> 21:53.379
I didn't know
you threatened to stab

21:53.410 --> 21:56.504
a teacher.
