21:56.540 --> 21:58.349
Well, so? They didn't offer me
any context.

21:58.380 --> 22:00.416
They just asked me
if I would prosecute a woman

22:00.450 --> 22:03.044
for threatening to stab a
teacher, and, yes, oddly enough,

22:03.080 --> 22:06.345
I said yes. I-I didn't know
it was about you.

22:06.390 --> 22:08.915
Then correct it.

22:08.960 --> 22:11.428
Correct what?
Tell the Correspondent that

22:11.460 --> 22:13.121
you know what
I wrote was a joke,

22:13.160 --> 22:16.129
and that they were wrong
to take it out of context.

22:16.160 --> 22:19.459
Ah, are we not friends
anymore, Frank?

22:19.500 --> 22:21.798
Wait a minute. Our agreement
wasn't to help each other win.

22:21.840 --> 22:23.467
It was just
that we not fight dirty.

22:23.510 --> 22:25.102
And you did.
I didn't.

22:25.140 --> 22:26.732
I didn't know
what they were saying.

22:26.770 --> 22:28.806
Okay.

22:28.840 --> 22:31.604
Then let's just leave it there.

22:31.650 --> 22:34.778
So, you're gonna let
your handlers leak dirt on me,

22:34.820 --> 22:36.469
dirt you know isn't true?

22:36.520 --> 22:39.148
I have no knowledge that
my handlers did any such thing.

22:39.190 --> 22:41.511
Wow.

22:41.560 --> 22:44.620
So we're right back
